app-uninstall - Uninstall applications

USAGE:
    app-uninstall <app-name>

DESCRIPTION:
    Uninstall a specific application from the system.

ARGUMENTS:
    app-name
        Name of the application to uninstall (required)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-install-step-timeout SECONDS
        Timeout per uninstall step (default: 300)

EXAMPLES:
    app-uninstall my-app
